summary: Ever wanted to get some where quick just cant be arsed getting there excuse my french. well with bat teleport\'s you can get there in a flash.
descriptionHtml:
This mod is a package of bat file\'s.

this mod allows you to quickly travel to places that you cant be bothered walking to or maby havent got on map, this Mod has a good amount of bat teleport\'s that are still been added to.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version .1
--------------------------------------------------------------- Skyrim -----------------------------------------------------------------
\"bluepalace\"  -  teleport\'s you to the blue palace in solitude
\"WRStables\"  -  teleport\'s you to the stables in whiterun
\"breezehome\"  -  teleport\'s you to your house in whiterun, breezehome
\"dawnstar\"  -  teleport\'s you to the Jarl\'s Longhouse in dawnstar
\"delphine\"  -  teleport\'s you to Delphine NPC
\"dragonsreach\"  -  teleport\'s you to the Jarl\'s Castle in whiterun Dragonsreach
\"esbern\"  -  teleport\'s you to Esbern NPC
\"falion\"  -  teleport\'s you to Falion NPC
\"honeyside\"  -  teleport\'s you to Your House in riften honeyside
\"morthal\"  -  teleport\'s you to the jarl\'s longhouse in morthal
\"proudspire\"  -  teleport\'s you to your house in solitude Proudspire manor
\"riverwood\"  -  teleport\'s you to Riverwood
\"RTStables\"  -  teleport\'s you to the Riften Stables
\"SilverBloodInn\"  -  teleport\'s you to the Silver Blood Inn In markarth
\"TeleportDelphine\"  -  teleport\'s Delphine to you
\"TeleportEsbern\"  -  teleport\'s Esbern to you
\"WHStables\"  -  teleport\'s you to the Windhelm Stables
\"Windhelm\"  -  teleport\'s you to the Palace of the kings in windhelm (Ulfric\'s Castle)
\"Winterhold\"  -  teleport\'s you to the jarl\'s Longhouse in Winterhold.
---------------------------------------------------------- Dawnguard ----------------------------------------------------------------
\"Serana\"  -  teleport\'s you to Serana NPC
\"Valerica\"  -  teleport\'s you to Valerica NPC
\"TeleportSerana\"  -  teleport\'s Serana NPC to you
\"TeleportValerica\"  -  teleport\'s Valerica NPC to you
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version .2
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Instruction\'s
Download - click download button
install - put in the Data folder
open game - run skyrimlauncher
open console - use the ` or the ~ button to bring up the console
type phrase - Bat breezehome   /   bat honeyside   /   bat delphine
close the console - repress `or the ~ button
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
EpiclyWhit3
